1
00:00:03,603 --> 00:00:05,338
Coming here to lecture me at this hour?

2
00:00:06,039 --> 00:00:06,940
You hungry?

3
00:00:07,407 --> 00:00:08,575
Starving.

4
00:00:14,014 --> 00:00:15,181
You have one of these too?

5
00:00:15,715 --> 00:00:16,216
What a coincidence.

6
00:00:16,216 --> 00:00:17,350
Mine is white,

7
00:00:17,350 --> 00:00:18,618
and yours is black.

8
00:00:18,618 --> 00:00:19,619
Where'd you get it?

9
00:00:26,459 --> 00:00:27,293
Hei Yan.

10
00:00:27,527 --> 00:00:28,962
I just found out you were the one

11
00:00:28,962 --> 00:00:30,897
who talked Mike into dropping Ko Shasha.

12
00:00:30,897 --> 00:00:32,265
It was just a suggestion.

13
00:00:32,265 --> 00:00:33,266
Are you out of your mind?

14
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:35,368
Replacing your own labelmate

15
00:00:35,368 --> 00:00:36,736
just to back someone from another agency?

16
00:00:37,170 --> 00:00:37,837
Like I said,

17
00:00:37,837 --> 00:00:38,638
I choose my rivals.

18
00:00:38,638 --> 00:00:40,373
I only shine when the competition is tough.

19
00:00:41,141 --> 00:00:42,308
I didn't want to miss the chance.

20
00:00:42,709 --> 00:00:43,710
Let me tell you,

21
00:00:44,077 --> 00:00:45,045
if you ever go behind my back

22
00:00:45,045 --> 00:00:46,279
to make decisions like that again,

23
00:00:46,679 --> 00:00:47,847
you'd better watch yourself.

24
00:00:57,457 --> 00:00:59,492
You chose your own manager,

25
00:00:59,492 --> 00:01:01,327
and you signed the contract yourself.

26
00:01:01,327 --> 00:01:02,462
You've still got a year and a half.

27
00:01:02,929 --> 00:01:04,164
Just tough it out.

28
00:01:32,592 --> 00:01:34,194
You're so unguarded.

29
00:01:39,132 --> 00:01:42,001
Subconscious reactions don't
change, no matter how long it's been.

30
00:01:43,736 --> 00:01:45,004
Did you also forget

31
00:01:46,005 --> 00:01:47,841
that you once called someone negative

32
00:01:49,109 --> 00:01:50,176
and insecure?
